(7211, 4277, 'rd_small_desc', 'Nancy is the Communication Specialist at METS who has previously worked at Makerere University, Tetea Uganda and NSSF in various capacities in the communication field. She is the recipient of the Cranimer Mugerwa Best Photojournalist Award 2010, She is passionate about photography, writing, Public Relations and events management.\r\n\r\nShe holds a Bachelor?s Degree in Mass Communication and a Master?s Degree in International Relations and Diplomatic Studies from Makerere University. She has gained extensive experience in the Communication sector spanning over seven years. Her passion for detail and excellence topped with perseverance makes her well suited for a fast-paced events environment.'),
