(8019, 1, '2016-10-09 09:05:04', '2016-10-09 09:05:04', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<blockquote><em>METS has offered technical Support to 48 CDC supported Districts on improved data use among District Health Teams (DHTs). The DHTs were trained to develop quarterly HIV and AIDS bulletins which highlight District performance, innovations and challenges encountered. Our aim is to ensure that DHT continue to produce these Bulletins on their own in the future to enable continued M&amp;E of HIV response</em></blockquote>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][blog_sc posts_per_page="15" type="type4" column="blog_3_col" category="bullentin" blog_heading_color="#81d742" blog_hl_color="#dd3333" blog_hover_color="#dd3333" blog_click="15"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Bulletins', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bulletins', '', '', '2016-10-11 05:24:08', '2016-10-11 05:24:08', '', 0, 'http://mets.or.ug/?page_id=8019', 0, 'page', '', 0),
