(8082, 1, '2016-10-09 16:22:12', '2016-10-09 16:22:12', 'Retention in HIV care among pregnant women on Antiretroviral Therapy (ART) is moderate in comparison to initiation. This summarised article put together by METS staff looks at Socio-demographic characteristics and justification of the big difference between the initiation and retention rates.', 'Retention in care among HIV-infected pregnant mothers', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'retention-in-care-among-hiv-infected-pregnant-mothers-on-life-long-antiretroviral-therapy-art-in-uganda-2', '', '', '2016-10-09 16:25:13', '2016-10-09 16:25:13', '', 0, 'http://mets.or.ug/?p=8082', 0, 'post', '', 0),
