(8469, 2, '2017-01-27 13:27:21', '2017-01-27 13:27:21', 'In line with our mandate to support CQI for SMC services, the M&amp;E Project will conduct a joint on-site mentorship and quality assessments for all the 57 CDC supported VMMC sites in Uganda. This activity is intended to;\r\n\r\ni) assess the quality of SMC services offered at each site using the MOH SMC Quality assessment tool,\r\n\r\nii) identify SMC service quality gaps and develop action plans for continuous quality improvement,\r\n\r\niii) collect data on TT vaccination,\r\n\r\niv) SMC data validation for the period October-December 2016.\r\n\r\nThe visits will be jointly conducted with the supporting IPs and MoH.', 'SMC Quality Improvement Assessment and Mentorship', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'smc-quality-improvement-assessment-and-mentorship', '', '', '2017-01-27 13:27:21', '2017-01-27 13:27:21', '', 0, 'http://mets.or.ug/?post_type=ajde_events&#038;p=8469', 0, 'ajde_events', '', 0),
