(8473, 1, '2017-01-30 06:08:08', '2017-01-30 06:08:08', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="Read online or Download our <strong>Quarterly</strong> Newsletter" google_fonts="font_family:Lato%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:300%20light%20regular%3A300%3Anormal"][vc_accordion][vc_accordion_tab title="2016 First, Second and Third quoter"][vc_column_text]Greetings from METS\r\n\r\nThe Program has rolled out well and this year it comes with the promise of great growth and change. As part of our own expansion and growth, we are excited to launch our first issue and we hope that you find it enlightening, we will continue to update you on our ongoing projects as the year rolls out. Please share or tell a friend to tell a friend.\r\n\r\n<a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=0BzMWf_9ra12sdlh3Z3NjOWZ3NTFHX0g2Qy12SlNMV00zSGRR">READ or DOWNLOAD PDF FILE HERE</a>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="2016 OpenMRS Newsletter "][vc_column_text]The 2016 OpenMRS International Implementers'' Conference was held in Uganda in December 2016. This <a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B4jwP0ShI6fCM19Hb1paMlUxbGs">Newsletter </a>highlights the events and activities of the six day conference at the Speke Resort Munyonyo[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][/vc_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Newsletters', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'newsletters', '', '', '2017-03-27 09:08:26', '2017-03-27 09:08:26', '', 0, 'http://mets.or.ug/?page_id=8473', 0, 'page', '', 0),
