(8794, 2, '2017-04-07 13:25:13', '2017-04-07 13:25:13', 'Stephen Ocaya has a Bachelor of Science in Computer Science and Now pursuing a Masters of Science in Data Communication and Software Engineering at Makerere University. With over 8 years experience in Health Information Systems and Software Systems, Stephen has mastered all aspects of solid software development life cycle for Health Systems. He was one of first people to customize District Health Information Systems (DHIS2) in Uganda, iHRIS, and other health systems.\r\n\r\nHe has major skills of Java Programming, Python, PHP, PostgreSQL, MySQL, MS SQL.\r\n\r\nEmail: stephocay@musph.ac.ug', 'Stephen Ocaya', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'stephen-ocaya', '', '', '2017-04-10 11:03:34', '2017-04-10 11:03:34', '', 0, 'http://mets.or.ug/?post_type=team-member&#038;p=8794', 0, 'team-member', '', 0),
